  • Classes in de.tudarmstadt.ukp.jwktl.api used by de.tudarmstadt.ukp.jwktl 
    Class and Description
    IWiktionaryCollection
    Models a list of multiple Wiktionary language editions (e.g., the English and the German Wiktionary editions).
    IWiktionaryEdition
    Models a single Wiktionary language edition (e.g., the English Wiktionary) for which this interface provides multiple querying and iteration methods.
  • Classes in de.tudarmstadt.ukp.jwktl.api used by de.tudarmstadt.ukp.jwktl.api 
    Class and Description
    IPronunciation
    Pronunciation information for IWiktionaryEntrys.
    IPronunciation.PronunciationType
    Types of different pronunciation information used by IPronunciation.getType().
    IQuotation
    Represents a quotation.
    IWikiString
    Represents a text that contains wiki markup.
    IWiktionary
    Base interface for the Wiktionary language edition and collection modelling common methods for querying and iterating over the encoded entries.
    IWiktionaryEdition
    Models a single Wiktionary language edition (e.g., the English Wiktionary) for which this interface provides multiple querying and iteration methods.
    IWiktionaryEntry
    A IWiktionaryEntry corresponds to a lexical entry.
    IWiktionaryExample 
    IWiktionaryPage
    A IWiktionaryPage corresponds to a unique URL of Wiktionary.
    IWiktionaryRelation
    Represents a paradigmatic relation between lexical entries or word senses.
    IWiktionaryRelation.LinkType
    Types of a link used by IWiktionaryRelation.getLinkType().
    IWiktionarySense
    A IWiktionarySense represents one word sense of a lexical entry (also called a lexical unit).
    IWiktionaryTranslation
    Represents a lexical translation of a IWiktionarySense.
    IWiktionaryWordForm
    Represents an (inflected) word form of a IWiktionaryEntry.
    PartOfSpeech
    Generic representation of the parts of speech used in Wiktionary.
    RelationType
    Represents the relation types used for IWiktionaryRelations.
    WiktionaryFormatter
    Utility class for producing simple string representations for the most commonly used JWKTL data objects.
